         "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgBering\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBering', '0%')\" src=\"images/ElSalvadorMuseo/Bering.jpg\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 6</b>: A map showing Indigenous migration routes across the Bering Strait. Photo taken at the Museo Nacional de Antropología en San Salvador, El Salvador (<htcite0>), on <htdate0>.</p>",
